{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|叀|又|c1=p|c2=s|t1=spindle|t2=hand|ls=ic|ls2=psc}} – a hand turning a spindle or spinning wheel. It has come to mean to bundle several things together into one. Originally also written {{zh-l|*叀}}.

The {{zh-l|*又}} was later replaced by related {{zh-l|*寸}}.

